      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "B\xF6lgedeki y\xFCr\xFCy\xFC\u015F park\u0131nda bulunan bir vatanda\u015Ftan
    yang\u0131n ihbar\u0131 al\u0131nd\u0131. Arayan ki\u015Fi durumu \u015F\xF6yle
    aktar\u0131yor: \"Park\u0131n tam orta k\u0131sm\u0131ndaki \xFC\xE7 a\u011Fa\xE7
    alev ald\u0131! A\u015F\u0131r\u0131 s\u0131caklar nedeniyle ate\u015F, di\u011Fer
    a\u011Fa\xE7lara do\u011Fru h\u0131zla yay\u0131lmaya ba\u015Flad\u0131.\" B\xF6lgeye
    ilk m\xFCdahale bekleniyor."
